      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks. i was worried it might be something bad like my heart or something since it feels kinda heavy in my chest sometimes when i'm breathless. but you think it's just aging/fitness? i don't really want to go to the doctor if i don't have to, it's such a hassle. if i take those extra puffs, how long until i should feel better?",
