      "content": "okay i'll try the extra puffs. but what if i start feeling even more dizzy or if the heaviness in my chest gets really sharp? i'm still pretty nervous about it. should i just keep taking the salbutamol or is there something else i can take at home to stop the chest pain if it gets worse?",
